{"tid":595076,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【超人退休】冇樓唔結婚論？李嘉誠寸爆港女「叫佢趁後生搵第二個！」","createTime":"2018-03-16T11:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T12:15:07.000Z","uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9bb902869465a95513c7adf7434d46298fecccae","tid":595076,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T11:17:01.000Z","msg":"香港樓價高企，市民難以負擔，即將退休的長和系主席李嘉誠為一眾年青男士講說話，他舉例子說，現時有女士跟大學未還畢業的男朋友說：「如果冇樓唔同你結婚，如果有咁嘅諗法，如果我做男呢，我會同佢（女仔）講，你趁而家後生，你快啲搵第二個！」<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠認為，買樓問題太注重都唔好，冇樓就不結婚這個說法不正常，「大學都未畢業，你就講，冇樓唔結婚，呢個係不正常！」<br />\n他又重申，要解決香港住屋問題，「要猛起多啲公屋同居屋！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180316/57955792\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180316%2F57955792&d=mtiUfB9ZA3VS0CGbD5RfylKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=5341126a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180316%2F57955792&h=c943b20d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180316/57955792</a><br />\n<br />\n垃圾廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 知唔知咩叫樓高潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43c441045b74b13d804d66409e60ef7426ccb71","tid":595076,"uid":104965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T11:20:30.000Z","msg":"其實佢答得好正路<br />\n不過好多人做10、20 年都追唔到上車"},{"pid":"a3d5ec231d6e61f14cb54493b03b34f4fe0c26be","tid":595076,"uid":62842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T12:15:07.000Z","msg":"港女：李嘉誠呢d廢老冇上進心"}]}